edegarike ( kannada : ಎದೆಗಾರಿಕೆ ; english : guts ) is a 2012 indian kannada crime drama film directed by sumana kittur , based on the novel of the same name written by agni shridhar .   it stars aditya in the lead role .   atul kulkarni , achyuth kumar , srujan lokesh , dharma and aakanksha mansukhani feature in supporting roles .   the film is based on the real-life incidents that occurred in the 1990s and is about cult figures in the karnataka underworld such as sridhar , muthappa rai and bachchan .   the film opened to widespread critical acclaim upon theatrical release .   it won the special jury award at the 6th bangalore international film festival .